title: Dave Hughes Is Handy
description:
Dave Hughes is probably one of Australia's best recognised comedians. His humour is VERY Australian, ie self-depricating, but he's as polished as a Christmas bauble. He's an everyday bloke but he can make the ordinary quite extraordinary.

These vids are MP4's @ 720x404 resolution (2400kbps). I have remastered the audio, amplified it to -2dB and rendered it at 448kbps (to preserve the integrity of the remaster).

I hope you enjoy this. It really is great stuff.

Cheers,
MoofieMan.
